  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ASCENDING INFERNO</strong> is your ultimate goal in this gorgeous, challenging-but-fair 2.5D precision platformer with a ball.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playing as Dani, it’s not enough to run, jump and platform your way out of Hell - you’ll need to dribble, kick and header her dead brother Vincent’s ball-shaped soul along with you!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just be sure you don’t fumble the ball - the depths of Hell is a long way to fall… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/14577b010ffe952a5bbf51e732174144.poster.avif?t=1762826401\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/14577b010ffe952a5bbf51e732174144.webm?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/14577b010ffe952a5bbf51e732174144.mp4?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/9de1bc5b2b5d1ccf5dd9977e4f310674.avif?t=1762826401\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Master precision platforming</u></strong> with a ball (actually your brother’s soul). </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Bask in a handcrafted world</u></strong> of gorgeous pixel and voxel art. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Ascend nine challenging layers</u></strong> of a modernized Dante’s Inferno. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Tackle unique mechanics</u></strong> in each layer of Hell - Limbo, Lust, Gluttony and beyond. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Take your time or beat the clock</u></strong> in a game built with speedrunners in mind. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Uncover a hidden story</u></strong> scattered across secret rooms in each level. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Unlock free cosmetics</u></strong> for Dani and Vincent by completing in-game challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><u>Checkpoint Mode</u></strong> exists for players who want to experience Ascending Inferno without the Foddian difficulty! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/89606a806da08ec4fad11c1b5af6cc57.avif?t=1762826401\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet Dani: she is a goth.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet Vincent: he currently has no legs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They're a sibling duo that belongs in heaven... except they're trapped in hell. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/af4ec6cacb23ecbc51a6e682908e926c.avif?t=1762826401\" width=600 height=261 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game takes place after Vincent's recent death, and unfortunately as fate would have it, Dani dies shortly after in an accident. She then awakens in the afterlife in which she finds the soul of her brother Vincent. During this reunion, Dani quickly discovers that they are trapped in Limbo and so the pair settle on the common goal of <strong><u>ASCENDING INFERNO</u></strong>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore secret rooms to uncover the deeper story and relationship dramas surrounding these siblings. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/d5167773acf0cd816007455d5dd80d72.poster.avif?t=1762826401\" width=598 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/d5167773acf0cd816007455d5dd80d72.webm?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/d5167773acf0cd816007455d5dd80d72.mp4?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/4c3fe47be139b30c9c2c0bc70216e089.avif?t=1762826401\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vincent cannot <strong>ASCEND INFERNO</strong> without you. Thank heavens he's conveniently shaped like a soccer ball... with eyes. You’ll have to kick, header, juggle and jump your way out of Inferno. As you ascend, each layer of Inferno will fight to keep you down in mechanically unique ways, so make sure to stay on your toes!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three words of advice: <strong>Don't. Fall. Down.</strong> The smallest mistake can be costly, and Vincent won’t hesitate to berate you when you fail. What else is a younger brother for? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/5db5c1039675de406db048ca9f9699c7.poster.avif?t=1762826401\" width=200 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/5db5c1039675de406db048ca9f9699c7.webm?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/5db5c1039675de406db048ca9f9699c7.mp4?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/2c8eb8a868295eceaf8ba6e45a0e7e77.poster.avif?t=1762826401\" width=200 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/2c8eb8a868295eceaf8ba6e45a0e7e77.webm?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/2c8eb8a868295eceaf8ba6e45a0e7e77.mp4?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/97dd7dd93f7d2968a69fea9b39e5c726.poster.avif?t=1762826401\" width=200 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/97dd7dd93f7d2968a69fea9b39e5c726.webm?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/97dd7dd93f7d2968a69fea9b39e5c726.mp4?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/45102c038ea3016f2dd161c2cd6aae78.avif?t=1762826401\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Does all that sound like to much? Well fear not weary traveler, we've just added a new game mode called Checkpoint Mode! <br><br>This mode is designed for people who want to experience the wonders of Ascending Inferno, without the Foddian difficulty. Activate checkpoints as you ascend, doing so will make you reset to that point in your climb whenever you fall below it! No more falling back to limbo for the 50th time<i> (Maybe)</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/e2e38b9763d30cee35fa1707a4230039.avif?t=1762826401\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hellishly Beautiful, each layer of Inferno is meticulously handcrafted in a stunning voxel and pixel art-style with a modern twist:   </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Limbo is a forgotten, rundown castle.   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Lust is a modern, grungy nightclub.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Gluttony is a trashed fast-food diner.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > And many more surprises for you to experience yourself!  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/a9fbe922da57b6c3e0c17cd7647d5974.avif?t=1762826401\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dani and Vincent are ready for kickoff. Do <strong><u>YOU</u></strong> have what it takes to achieve your goal of <strong>ASCENDING INFERNO?</strong> Or will you be forever lost in Limbo…  </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ASCENDING INFERNO</strong> is your ultimate goal in this gorgeous, challenging-but-fair 2.5D precision platformer with a ball.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playing as Dani, it’s not enough to run, jump and platform your way out of Hell - you’ll need to dribble, kick and header her dead brother Vincent’s ball-shaped soul along with you!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just be sure you don’t fumble the ball - the depths of Hell is a long way to fall… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/14577b010ffe952a5bbf51e732174144.poster.avif?t=1762826401\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/14577b010ffe952a5bbf51e732174144.webm?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/14577b010ffe952a5bbf51e732174144.mp4?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/9de1bc5b2b5d1ccf5dd9977e4f310674.avif?t=1762826401\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Master precision platforming</u></strong> with a ball (actually your brother’s soul). </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Bask in a handcrafted world</u></strong> of gorgeous pixel and voxel art. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Ascend nine challenging layers</u></strong> of a modernized Dante’s Inferno. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Tackle unique mechanics</u></strong> in each layer of Hell - Limbo, Lust, Gluttony and beyond. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Take your time or beat the clock</u></strong> in a game built with speedrunners in mind. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Uncover a hidden story</u></strong> scattered across secret rooms in each level. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Unlock free cosmetics</u></strong> for Dani and Vincent by completing in-game challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><u>Checkpoint Mode</u></strong> exists for players who want to experience Ascending Inferno without the Foddian difficulty! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/89606a806da08ec4fad11c1b5af6cc57.avif?t=1762826401\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet Dani: she is a goth.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet Vincent: he currently has no legs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They're a sibling duo that belongs in heaven... except they're trapped in hell. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/af4ec6cacb23ecbc51a6e682908e926c.avif?t=1762826401\" width=600 height=261 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game takes place after Vincent's recent death, and unfortunately as fate would have it, Dani dies shortly after in an accident. She then awakens in the afterlife in which she finds the soul of her brother Vincent. During this reunion, Dani quickly discovers that they are trapped in Limbo and so the pair settle on the common goal of <strong><u>ASCENDING INFERNO</u></strong>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore secret rooms to uncover the deeper story and relationship dramas surrounding these siblings. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/d5167773acf0cd816007455d5dd80d72.poster.avif?t=1762826401\" width=598 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/d5167773acf0cd816007455d5dd80d72.webm?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/d5167773acf0cd816007455d5dd80d72.mp4?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/4c3fe47be139b30c9c2c0bc70216e089.avif?t=1762826401\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vincent cannot <strong>ASCEND INFERNO</strong> without you. Thank heavens he's conveniently shaped like a soccer ball... with eyes. You’ll have to kick, header, juggle and jump your way out of Inferno. As you ascend, each layer of Inferno will fight to keep you down in mechanically unique ways, so make sure to stay on your toes!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three words of advice: <strong>Don't. Fall. Down.</strong> The smallest mistake can be costly, and Vincent won’t hesitate to berate you when you fail. What else is a younger brother for? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/5db5c1039675de406db048ca9f9699c7.poster.avif?t=1762826401\" width=200 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/5db5c1039675de406db048ca9f9699c7.webm?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/5db5c1039675de406db048ca9f9699c7.mp4?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/2c8eb8a868295eceaf8ba6e45a0e7e77.poster.avif?t=1762826401\" width=200 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/2c8eb8a868295eceaf8ba6e45a0e7e77.webm?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/2c8eb8a868295eceaf8ba6e45a0e7e77.mp4?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/97dd7dd93f7d2968a69fea9b39e5c726.poster.avif?t=1762826401\" width=200 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/97dd7dd93f7d2968a69fea9b39e5c726.webm?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/97dd7dd93f7d2968a69fea9b39e5c726.mp4?t=1762826401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/45102c038ea3016f2dd161c2cd6aae78.avif?t=1762826401\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Does all that sound like to much? Well fear not weary traveler, we've just added a new game mode called Checkpoint Mode! <br><br>This mode is designed for people who want to experience the wonders of Ascending Inferno, without the Foddian difficulty. Activate checkpoints as you ascend, doing so will make you reset to that point in your climb whenever you fall below it! No more falling back to limbo for the 50th time<i> (Maybe)</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/e2e38b9763d30cee35fa1707a4230039.avif?t=1762826401\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hellishly Beautiful, each layer of Inferno is meticulously handcrafted in a stunning voxel and pixel art-style with a modern twist:   </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Limbo is a forgotten, rundown castle.   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Lust is a modern, grungy nightclub.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Gluttony is a trashed fast-food diner.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > And many more surprises for you to experience yourself!  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2442820/extras/a9fbe922da57b6c3e0c17cd7647d5974.avif?t=1762826401\" width=620 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dani and Vincent are ready for kickoff. Do <strong><u>YOU</u></strong> have what it takes to achieve your goal of <strong>ASCENDING INFERNO?</strong> Or will you be forever lost in Limbo…  </p>",
